+============================================================
+Kanavana – Pilot Environment
+============================================================
+
+This repository is a **sanitized mirror** of the pilot environment
+used in EU project application work carried out by Kanavana.
+It is built on the Massively theme (HTML5UP) and extended with AI-driven prototypes.
+
+### Prototypes included
+
+1. **common_sense.php**  
+   - “Common Sense Agent” MVP  
+   - Prompt-driven planning with safety guardrails  
+   - Interruptible goal execution  
+   - JSON API with minimal browser UI  
+
+2. **jobs.html**  
+   - AI-assisted multilingual job and web search  
+   - Combines GPT with Tavily search API  
+   - Explores opportunities across languages and regions  
+
+3. **play.php**  
+   - AI-assisted text rephrasing playground  
+   - Transform input into various expression styles (formal, casual, persuasive, etc.)  
+   - Useful for communication training and experimentation  
+
+### Access
+All prototypes are hosted under: [https://pilot.kanavana.fi/](https://pilot.kanavana.fi/)  
+API key is provided via `.htaccess` (SetEnv OPENAI_API_KEY).
+
+### Contribution
+This repo is maintained as a read-only mirror (no secrets).  
+Patch contributions are welcome via unified diffs (`git diff > patch-x.diff`).  
+
+Developed by **Kanavana** – for EU pilot demonstration.
